<p><strong>Operational Insight</strong>: iOS CAC in North America is typically 40%-60% higher than Android, but conversion to paying users is also nearly double. For publishers with sufficient budgets, focusing on iOS is recommended. Although initial costs are higher, <strong>long-term LTV performance is more stable</strong>.</p>
