</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>💡 <strong>Practical Advice</strong>: For <strong>mid-core RPG or strategy games</strong>, Eastern Europe's cost-effective users can effectively reduce overall CAC. For monetization targeting Western European ARPU, Eastern European users require careful LTV-adjusted value assessment.</p>
