<p><strong>Optimization Focus</strong>: For casual games, CAC optimization core lies in <strong>creative assets</strong> and <strong>placement selection</strong>. TikTok and Meta's Reels short video placements show significantly better CPI performance than traditional Feed for these game types.</p>
