<h2>Part 4: Deep Analysis of Core Factors Affecting CAC</h2>
<h3>1. Ad Creative Quality (Weight: 35%)</h3>
<p>Creative assets are the primary determinant for click-through and conversion rates. High-quality creatives can:</p>
<ul>
<li>Boost CTR by 20%-50%</li>
<li>Reduce CVR by 15%-30%</li>
<li>Indirectly lower CPI (cost per install)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>High-Performance Creative Characteristics</strong>:</p>
<blockquote>
