- Real gameplay footage (not rendered images)<br />
- Clear benefit demonstration ("Get rare characters FREE")<br />
- Social proof elements ("1M players are playing")<br />
- Urgency creation (countdown, limited-time events)</p>
</blockquote>
<h3>2. Audience Targeting Strategy (Weight: 25%)</h3>
<p>Too broad: Excessive invalid impressions, CAC soars<br />
Too narrow: Insufficient volume, volatile costs</p>
<p><strong>Best Practices</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Cold Start Phase</strong>: Use Broad targeting to accumulate data</li>
<li><strong>Optimization Phase</strong>: Expand based on converted user Lookalikes</li>
<li><strong>Stabilization Phase</strong>: Use Custom Audiences to exclude already converted users</li>
</ol>
